\n教聯會也發表聲明，指氣異常嚴寒，呼籲教育局明天除讓全港小學、幼稚園、幼兒中心及特殊學校停課一天外，中學亦應准學生毋需穿著校服上課。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"27d21e268c2229a65cce2b0a33dd28d15eb029b1","tid":502031,"uid":68483,"like":62,"dislike":8,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"傻仔，真係報得警架"},{"pid":"d26abd7ebc0b68c018b083c3f5b1a93da0b3c917","tid":502031,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"記者朋友大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48534e233c3daafbe61eaaeb47485e047265e013","tid":502031,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"點解會犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申無知撚"},{"pid":"1defcc3d0f2309864a85dfa7fb48c31b6fbe1130","tid":502031,"uid":73089,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申無知撚</blockquote><br />\n有撚咩 放晒日子喺到"},{"pid":"2fc5ec3fbbab9722857b693a7dc52059649f14a1","tid":502031,"uid":33439,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申無知撚</blockquote><br />\n散報虛假消息引致恐慌+不誠實使用電腦"},{"pid":"fceac2e2dbf42a57a5bc1e7ce749f2a3e2efa67f","tid":502031,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"On 撚鳩"},{"pid":"696da3f15e0714d959e3ac74ebc05dadc8f99399","tid":502031,"uid":18968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 家屬謝禮 )"},{"pid":"c156a8086405074d51cd15eac8c596daa7703169","tid":502031,"uid":126952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"引致大眾恐慌就ok"},{"pid":"ef4fc5185504ccb56a994ddd8bb046fded14d0ab","tid":502031,"uid":54137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score